            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Last year we moved to this school, Teachers give great support for my kids to adapt the new environment. They are very student friendly. Apart from academic they encourage the kids to actively participate in the extra curricular activities.... The campus is hygiene and well maintained especially the classroom and toilets...\nMy special thanks to the class teacher Rabiya mam (5c) and kavitha mam(8B) and all the other teacher who gave a moral support for my kids... The main thing is I can easily reach the teacher all the time. The communication between the teacher and parents are too good..\nMy thanks to all the members in the RISHS family...",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
