          "reviewBody": "An amazing school. The teachers are Professional,well organised and very much caring. The management is open minded and thinks unconventionally in making a successful educational experience for their students. RISHS teachers have a good bond with their students. They teach valuable lessons, communication life lessons and many more!",
          "publisher": {
