            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "“Fantastic school! The teachers are Professional, caring and well organized. The management is open minded and think outside the box to make a successful educational experience for the students. RISHS teachers are committed to each and every child. They teach value lessons, communication and leadership skills. admissions process was outstanding, they really care and truly want the best for your child.”",
          "publisher": {
