          },
          "datePublished": "2023-05-04",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Rishs International School always been an extraordinary Institution in up bringing students, making them confident disciplined & transforming them as leaders for better future.\nUndoubtedly the school has the best infrastructure, lab facilities, library & various extra curricular activities.\nThe teachers are really good & dedicated, professional & caring.\nThe admission process was outstanding.\nThe students learn new things each & everyday. The students learn the concepts in activity based learning & do way method.\nWell planned & organized Academic Programs.\nThe Management of the school not only focus the Academic part they are taking the endless efforts to bring the students talents.\nThe students participating in a various of activities & events.\nCo-curricular activities organised by the school helped the students to develop confidence & over come stage fear. So, Students gets ample opportunities to explore & progress in all aspects. The school focused on Communication & Social skills have enhanced a lot due to a range of classroom activities.\nRishs is a Right way to start your Child Early Education.\n\"School for a choice, not for a chance\".",
